Anglian Water Appoints Tim Stone as Director, Independent Says

-- B y   R a c h e l   G r a h a m
-- 
2011-10-16T11:28:07Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-16/anglian-water-appoints-tim-stone-as-director-independent-says.html
Anglian Water Services Ltd.  has
appointed Tim Stone as a non-executive director, the Independent
on Sunday  said , citing Chairman Adrian Montague.  Stone is an adviser to the U.K. government on the nuclear
industry, according to the report.  To contact the reporter on this story:
